{
  "video_id": "B43f89Y9f-A",
  "title": "How to connect with depressed friends | Bill Bernat",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12690.0,
      "end_time": 18481.0,
      "text": "The one conversation that uplifted me more than any other in my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18505.0,
      "end_time": 20924.0,
      "text": "was with a woman who told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20949.0,
      "end_time": 22694.0,
      "text": "how, a few days earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22718.0,
      "end_time": 26823.0,
      "text": "she drove her Jeep Wrangler to the edge of the Grand Canyon"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26847.0,
      "end_time": 29604.0,
      "text": "and sat there, revving the engine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29628.0,
      "end_time": 31365.0,
      "text": "thinking about driving over."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32655.0,
      "end_time": 35377.0,
      "text": "Even though I had severe social anxiety,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35401.0,
      "end_time": 38350.0,
      "text": "in that conversation, I was totally at ease."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38590.0,
      "end_time": 39559.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39584.0,
      "end_time": 42267.0,
      "text": "She told me what was going on in her life"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42291.0,
      "end_time": 44593.0,
      "text": "in the days and months leading up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44617.0,
      "end_time": 46849.0,
      "text": "what her thoughts were at that exact moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46873.0,
      "end_time": 48361.0,
      "text": "why she wanted to die,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48386.0,
      "end_time": 49631.0,
      "text": "and why she didn&#39;t do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50271.0,
      "end_time": 53530.0,
      "text": "We nodded and half-smiled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53770.0,
      "end_time": 55701.0,
      "text": "and then it was my turn to talk about my journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55725.0,
      "end_time": 60371.0,
      "text": "to a dining table in the hygienic community area"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60395.0,
      "end_time": 63891.0,
      "text": "of the mental health wing of a mountain-town hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64503.0,
      "end_time": 66200.0,
      "text": "I took too many sleeping pills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66440.0,
      "end_time": 67750.0,
      "text": "and after they treated me for that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67774.0,
      "end_time": 73605.0,
      "text": "they were like, \"Hey, we would love it if you would be our guest"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73629.0,
      "end_time": 75123.0,
      "text": "in the psych ward.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75147.0,
      "end_time": 80200.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80597.0,
      "end_time": 85643.0,
      "text": "We joked that her suicide would have made a way better postcard."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85668.0,
      "end_time": 86726.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86750.0,
      "end_time": 88134.0,
      "text": "We talked shop."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88448.0,
      "end_time": 89869.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89894.0,
      "end_time": 92353.0,
      "text": "She allowed me to be deeply depressed"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92377.0,
      "end_time": 97170.0,
      "text": "and have a genuine connection to another person, simultaneously."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97789.0,
      "end_time": 98947.0,
      "text": "For the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98971.0,
      "end_time": 102145.0,
      "text": "I identified as somebody living with depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102169.0,
      "end_time": 103877.0,
      "text": "and I felt good about it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103901.0,
      "end_time": 106180.0,
      "text": "like I was wasn&#39;t a bad person for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106918.0,
      "end_time": 111690.0,
      "text": "Now imagine one of the people at that table was a member of your family"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111930.0,
      "end_time": 113300.0,
      "text": "or a close friend."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113270.0,
      "end_time": 115300.0,
      "text": "Would you be comfortable talking to them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115447.0,
      "end_time": 117526.0,
      "text": "What if instead of the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117550.0,
      "end_time": 119770.0,
      "text": "they were at your kitchen table"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 119101.0,
      "end_time": 121160.0,
      "text": "and told you they were really depressed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 122295.0,
      "end_time": 124622.0,
      "text": "The World Health Organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124646.0,
      "end_time": 131200.0,
      "text": "says that depression is the leading cause of ill health and disability worldwide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 131440.0,
      "end_time": 134122.0,
      "text": "affecting 350 million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 134146.0,
      "end_time": 136410.0,
      "text": "The National Institute of Mental Health"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136660.0,
      "end_time": 140717.0,
      "text": "reports seven percent of Americans experiencing depression in a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141840.0,
      "end_time": 143822.0,
      "text": "So depression is super common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 143846.0,
      "end_time": 146523.0,
      "text": "yet in my experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146547.0,
      "end_time": 149513.0,
      "text": "most folks don&#39;t want to talk to depressed people"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 149537.0,
      "end_time": 151378.0,
      "text": "unless we pretend to be happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 153395.0,
      "end_time": 157310.0,
      "text": "A cheerful facade is appropriate for casual interactions."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157550.0,
      "end_time": 161769.0,
      "text": "A depressed person can ask for extra syrup in their pumpkin spice latte"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 161793.0,
      "end_time": 163813.0,
      "text": "without explaining that they need it"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 163837.0,
      "end_time": 167905.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re trapped in the infinite darkness of their soul"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167930.0,
      "end_time": 169962.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve lost all hope of escape --"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 169986.0,
      "end_time": 170987.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 171110.0,
      "end_time": 172162.0,
      "text": "again."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 172186.0,
      "end_time": 175251.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 175275.0,
      "end_time": 178405.0,
      "text": "Depression doesn&#39;t diminish a person&#39;s desire"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 178429.0,
      "end_time": 180271.0,
      "text": "to connect with other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 180295.0,
      "end_time": 181662.0,
      "text": "just their ability."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 182460.0,
      "end_time": 185272.0,
      "text": "So in spite of what you might think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185296.0,
      "end_time": 187766.0,
      "text": "talking to friends and family living with depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187790.0,
      "end_time": 191257.0,
      "text": "can be really easy and maybe even fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191281.0,
      "end_time": 197150.0,
      "text": "Not, like, Facebook-selfie-with-Lady-Gaga- at-an-underground-party fun --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 197174.0,
      "end_time": 199190.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m talking about the kind of fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 199214.0,
      "end_time": 202370.0,
      "text": "where people enjoy each other&#39;s company effortlessly."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 203205.0,
      "end_time": 204587.0,
      "text": "Nobody feels awkward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 204611.0,
      "end_time": 209390.0,
      "text": "and no one accuses the sad person of ruining the holidays."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 210244.0,
      "end_time": 213971.0,
      "text": "Why does this chasm even exist?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 213995.0,
      "end_time": 215228.0,
      "text": "On the one side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 215252.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "you have people living with depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 217284.0,
      "end_time": 220545.0,
      "text": "who may act in off-putting or confusing ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 220569.0,
      "end_time": 223242.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re fighting a war in their head"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 223266.0,
      "end_time": 224809.0,
      "text": "that nobody else can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 225307.0,
      "end_time": 226529.0,
      "text": "On the other side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 228740.0,
      "end_time": 231570.0,
      "text": "the vast majority of people look across the chasm"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 231810.0,
      "end_time": 232232.0,
      "text": "and shake their heads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 232256.0,
      "end_time": 235272.0,
      "text": "like, \"Why you gotta be so depressed?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 236817.0,
      "end_time": 240457.0,
      "text": "You may recognize a divide like this in your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 241660.0,
      "end_time": 243550.0,
      "text": "Do you want to build a bridge across it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 243712.0,
      "end_time": 245856.0,
      "text": "You may not want to build a bridge --"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 245880.0,
      "end_time": 248475.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s a totally valid choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 249182.0,
      "end_time": 252660.0,
      "text": "Or maybe you&#39;d like to build a stronger connection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 252684.0,
      "end_time": 257134.0,
      "text": "but you have a lot of questions and concerns."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 257158.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260357.00000000003,
      "text": "You&#39;re what I might call \"bridge curious.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 260380.0,
      "end_time": 264664.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 264689.0,
      "end_time": 266123.0,
      "text": "Here are some possible reasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 266147.0,
      "end_time": 268736.0,
      "text": "why some of you may avoid depressed people."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 269807.0,
      "end_time": 271600.0,
      "text": "You might be afraid"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 271300.0,
      "end_time": 273724.0,
      "text": "that if you talk to somebody while they&#39;re depressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 273748.0,
      "end_time": 276409.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re suddenly responsible for their well-being."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 277521.0,
      "end_time": 280519.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not expected to be Dr. Phil."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 280965.0,
      "end_time": 282155.0,
      "text": "Just be friendly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 282180.0,
      "end_time": 283713.0,
      "text": "more like Ellen."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 283737.0,
      "end_time": 287213.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 287519.0,
      "end_time": 290540.0,
      "text": "You may worry that you won&#39;t know what to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 290564.0,
      "end_time": 294984.0,
      "text": "and every attempt at conversation will be awkward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 295800.0,
      "end_time": 297404.0,
      "text": "and the only time you&#39;ll feel comfortable"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 297428.0,
      "end_time": 299332.0,
      "text": "is when you both just give up on talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 299357.0,
      "end_time": 301220.0,
      "text": "and stare at your phones."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 302304.0,
      "end_time": 306544.0,
      "text": "Words are not the most important thing to focus on."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 307931.0,
      "end_time": 312193.0,
      "text": "You might fear seeing your shadow."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 312217.0,
      "end_time": 315582.0,
      "text": "Hey, if you have been successfully outrunning"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 315607.0,
      "end_time": 318700.0,
      "text": "your personal emotional demons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 318940.0,
      "end_time": 319865.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s awesome."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 320401.0,
      "end_time": 322393.0,
      "text": "May the wind be at your back."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 322417.0,
      "end_time": 323431.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 323456.0,
      "end_time": 327169.0,
      "text": "You can be the least woo-woo person in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 327193.0,
      "end_time": 329209.0,
      "text": "and still connect with depressed people."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 330477.0,
      "end_time": 333318.0,
      "text": "Maybe you&#39;ve heard that depression is contagious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 333342.0,
      "end_time": 335323.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re afraid of catching it."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 335347.0,
      "end_time": 337359.0,
      "text": "Bring some hand sanitizer."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 337383.0,
      "end_time": 338383.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 338408.0,
      "end_time": 342896.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re much more likely to catch the joy of human bonding."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 343657.0,
      "end_time": 345662.0,
      "text": "Maybe you see depressed people differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 345687.0,
      "end_time": 348955.0,
      "text": "You think of them as flawed or defective."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 350299.0,
      "end_time": 353306.0,
      "text": "Multiple university studies have shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 353331.0,
      "end_time": 357786.0,
      "text": "that A students are more likely to have bipolar condition."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 358705.0,
      "end_time": 361618.0,
      "text": "Our brains aren&#39;t broken or damaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 361642.0,
      "end_time": 363593.0,
      "text": "they just work differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 363617.0,
      "end_time": 369323.0,
      "text": "I spent a lot of years thinking happy people just don&#39;t get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369347.0,
      "end_time": 370494.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 370518.0,
      "end_time": 374143.0,
      "text": "I did eventually stop discriminating against happy people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 374167.0,
      "end_time": 377270.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 378433.0,
      "end_time": 381339.0,
      "text": "I began battling depression when I was eight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 381363.0,
      "end_time": 383510.0,
      "text": "and decades later, to my surprise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 383534.0,
      "end_time": 385108.0,
      "text": "I started winning."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 385132.0,
      "end_time": 389970.0,
      "text": "I shifted from being miserable much of the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 389121.0,
      "end_time": 391231.0,
      "text": "to enjoying life."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 391255.0,
      "end_time": 394425.0,
      "text": "I live pretty well with my bipolar condition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 394449.0,
      "end_time": 396928.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve overcome some other mental health conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 396952.0,
      "end_time": 400253.0,
      "text": "like overeating, addiction and social anxiety."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 400634.0,
      "end_time": 404297.0,
      "text": "So I live on both sides of this chasm."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 404974.0,
      "end_time": 409692.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m offering some guidance"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 409716.0,
      "end_time": 412425.0,
      "text": "based on my experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 412449.0,
      "end_time": 414758.0,
      "text": "to help you build a bridge across it"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 414782.0,
      "end_time": 416224.0,
      "text": "if you want to."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 416248.0,
      "end_time": 418195.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not hard science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 418220.0,
      "end_time": 422721.0,
      "text": "but I worked with a lot people I know who&#39;ve lived with depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 422745.0,
      "end_time": 424968.0,
      "text": "to refine these suggestions."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 426860.0,
      "end_time": 428650.0,
      "text": "First up, some things you might want to avoid --"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 428674.0,
      "end_time": 430150.0,
      "text": "some \"don&#39;ts.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 431213.0,
      "end_time": 434714.0,
      "text": "One of the most off-putting things you can say is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 434738.0,
      "end_time": 436300.0,
      "text": "\"Just get over it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 437411.0,
      "end_time": 439380.0,
      "text": "Great idea -- love it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 439404.0,
      "end_time": 441721.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s just we already thought of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 441745.0,
      "end_time": 448154.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 448178.0,
      "end_time": 452455.0,
      "text": "The absence of the ability to just get over it is depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 452479.0,
      "end_time": 456292.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 456316.0,
      "end_time": 461162.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 461186.0,
      "end_time": 464924.0,
      "text": "We feel it in our bodies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 464949.0,
      "end_time": 467354.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a physical thing for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 467378.0,
      "end_time": 469385.0,
      "text": "And medically it&#39;s no different"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 469409.0,
      "end_time": 471791.0,
      "text": "from telling someone with a broken ankle or cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 471815.0,
      "end_time": 473123.0,
      "text": "\"just get over it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 476477.0,
      "end_time": 479589.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t be hell-bent on fixing us."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 479613.0,
      "end_time": 483968.0,
      "text": "Like, thank you, but ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 483992.0,
      "end_time": 488327.0,
      "text": "the pressure can make us depressed people feel like we&#39;re disappointing you."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 488930.0,
      "end_time": 491791.0,
      "text": "Also, things that make some people feel better"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 491815.0,
      "end_time": 493542.0,
      "text": "may not work for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 493566.0,
      "end_time": 497224.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t cure clinical depression by getting ice cream ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 497949.0,
      "end_time": 501571.0,
      "text": "which is unfortunate, because that would be living the dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 501595.0,
      "end_time": 504456.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 505698.0,
      "end_time": 510731.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t take a negative response personally."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 511216.0,
      "end_time": 514899.0,
      "text": "So, I have a friend who, about a year ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 514923.0,
      "end_time": 518135.0,
      "text": "messaged me that he was really isolated and depressed."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 518602.0,
      "end_time": 521103.0,
      "text": "And I suggested some things for him to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 521128.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523461.00000000006,
      "text": "and he was like, \"No, no and no.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 523485.0,
      "end_time": 524636.0,
      "text": "And I got mad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 524660.0,
      "end_time": 528597.0,
      "text": "like, how dare he not embrace my brilliant wisdom?"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 528621.0,
      "end_time": 530337.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 530361.0,
      "end_time": 533827.0,
      "text": "And then I remembered times I&#39;ve been depressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 533851.0,
      "end_time": 538467.0,
      "text": "and how I thought I was doomed in all possible futures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 538491.0,
      "end_time": 542163.0,
      "text": "or everybody suddenly hated me, and things like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 543498.0,
      "end_time": 546717.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t matter how many people told me otherwise --"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 546741.0,
      "end_time": 548144.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t believe them."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 549220.0,
      "end_time": 552308.0,
      "text": "So I let my friend know I cared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 552332.0,
      "end_time": 554610.0,
      "text": "and I didn&#39;t take it personally."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 555956.0,
      "end_time": 561242.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t let a lack of bubbly happiness freak you out."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 561594.0,
      "end_time": 563175.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a shark attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 563648.0,
      "end_time": 566592.0,
      "text": "\"Call the coast guard, my friend is sad!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 566616.0,
      "end_time": 568278.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 568302.0,
      "end_time": 572550.0,
      "text": "We can be sad and OK at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 572835.0,
      "end_time": 574169.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to say that again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 574193.0,
      "end_time": 577794.0,
      "text": "because in our society, we&#39;re taught the opposite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 577818.0,
      "end_time": 579933.0,
      "text": "and so it&#39;s counterintuitive."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 580556.0,
      "end_time": 584834.0,
      "text": "People can be sad and OK at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 585819.0,
      "end_time": 588939.0,
      "text": "So some of these things may apply to you personally, some may not."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 588963.0,
      "end_time": 590113.0,
      "text": "Take what&#39;s useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 590728.0,
      "end_time": 594104.0,
      "text": "And remember, you don&#39;t have to connect."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 595609.0,
      "end_time": 597119.0,
      "text": "If you want to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 597143.0,
      "end_time": 599229.0,
      "text": "here are some suggestions that may help --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 599253.0,
      "end_time": 600403.0,
      "text": "some \"dos.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 601484.0,
      "end_time": 604358.0,
      "text": "Talk to us in your natural voice, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 604382.0,
      "end_time": 606813.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 606837.0,
      "end_time": 612910.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t need to put on a sad voice because we&#39;re depressed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 612115.0,
      "end_time": 615480.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t sneeze when you&#39;re talking to somebody with a cold."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 615720.0,
      "end_time": 618282.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 618306.0,
      "end_time": 620848.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not rude to be upbeat."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 620872.0,
      "end_time": 623455.0,
      "text": "You can be you, OK?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 623480.0,
      "end_time": 626377.0,
      "text": "If you make an offer to be there for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 626401.0,
      "end_time": 629161.0,
      "text": "clearly state what you can and can&#39;t do."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 629907.0,
      "end_time": 632381.0,
      "text": "I have told people, \"Hey, call or text any time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 632405.0,
      "end_time": 635391.0,
      "text": "but I might not be able to get back to you that same day.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 636221.0,
      "end_time": 639465.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s totally cool to not make an offer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 639489.0,
      "end_time": 643776.0,
      "text": "or to make a narrow offer with really clear boundaries around it."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 645258.0,
      "end_time": 647535.0,
      "text": "Give us a sense of control."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 650520.0,
      "end_time": 652410.0,
      "text": "Like, get our consent."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 652434.0,
      "end_time": 655314.0,
      "text": "I have a friend who, a while back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 655339.0,
      "end_time": 657427.0,
      "text": "when I was having a depressive episode,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 657451.0,
      "end_time": 660130.0,
      "text": "reached out and said, \"Hey, I want to check in with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 660154.0,
      "end_time": 661346.0,
      "text": "Can I call you every day?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 661370.0,
      "end_time": 663800.0,
      "text": "Maybe text you every day and call later in the week?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 663824.0,
      "end_time": 665155.0,
      "text": "What works for you?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 666409.0,
      "end_time": 669592.0,
      "text": "By getting my permission, she earned my complete confidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 669616.0,
      "end_time": 672583.0,
      "text": "and remains one of my best friends today."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 674189.0,
      "end_time": 676420.0,
      "text": "And my last suggestion is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 677562.0,
      "end_time": 680403.0,
      "text": "interact about not depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 680427.0,
      "end_time": 682553.0,
      "text": "aka, normal stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 682577.0,
      "end_time": 686314.0,
      "text": "I have a friend who, when people were worried about him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 686338.0,
      "end_time": 689300.0,
      "text": "they would call and ask if he wanted to go shopping"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 689540.0,
      "end_time": 691385.0,
      "text": "or help them clean out their garage."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 691920.0,
      "end_time": 694880.0,
      "text": "Your depressed friends could be a good source of free labor --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 694904.0,
      "end_time": 701904.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 704132.0,
      "end_time": 707464.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m really getting at is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 707489.0,
      "end_time": 712520.0,
      "text": "invite them to contribute to your life in some way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 712760.0,
      "end_time": 716607.0,
      "text": "even if it&#39;s as small as asking you to go see a movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 716631.0,
      "end_time": 718462.0,
      "text": "that you wanted to see in the theater."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 719588.0,
      "end_time": 723477.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s a lot of dos and don&#39;ts and maybes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 723501.0,
      "end_time": 726635.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s not by any means a definitive list."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 728146.0,
      "end_time": 730937.0,
      "text": "The thing to remember is that they&#39;re all grounded"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 730961.0,
      "end_time": 733273.0,
      "text": "in one guiding principle."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 733709.0,
      "end_time": 736439.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s what allowed the woman in the Jeep Wrangler"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 737725.0,
      "end_time": 741100.0,
      "text": "to start me on the path to recovery without even trying."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 741674.0,
      "end_time": 745420.0,
      "text": "She talked to me like I belonged"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 745660.0,
      "end_time": 749883.0,
      "text": "and contributed exactly as I was at that moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 751270.0,
      "end_time": 755877.0,
      "text": "If you talk to a depressed person as if their life is just as valuable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 755902.0,
      "end_time": 758344.0,
      "text": "intense and beautiful as yours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 758368.0,
      "end_time": 762298.0,
      "text": "then there&#39;s no need to build a bridge between you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 762322.0,
      "end_time": 764820.0,
      "text": "because you&#39;ve closed the chasm."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 765684.0,
      "end_time": 769492.0,
      "text": "Focus on that instead of your words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 771210.0,
      "end_time": 775380.0,
      "text": "and it may be the most uplifting conversation of their life."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 776568.0,
      "end_time": 779528.0,
      "text": "What could that do for somebody you care about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 780203.0,
      "end_time": 782528.0,
      "text": "What could it do for you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 783181.0,
      "end_time": 784332.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 784356.0,
      "end_time": 789277.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}